Class QueueAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.recyclerview.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<QueueAdapter.Holder>

  • public class QueueAdapter
extends RecyclerView.Adapter<QueueAdapter.Holder>
    List<MediaSessionCompat.QueueItem> adapter for a RecyclerView that each item's title, duration, and a play icon if it is the playing item.
